snippet.title: World of Warriors – Announce Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/world-of-warriors-ps4/ 

LET BATTLE COMMENCE!
History’s toughest warriors find themselves summoned to a land beyond our own. In this mysterious kingdom, known as the Wildlands, the only way to survive… is to fight!

Battle alone or alongside friends in a combat-focused adventure, as the epic World of Warriors™ universe from Mind Candy (creators of the global phenomenon Moshi Monsters™) makes its exclusive console debut on PlayStation®4.

Available March 21, 2018.

© 2018 Mind Candy Ltd. World of Warriors and the World of Warriors logo are trademarks of Mind Candy Ltd. All rights reserved. Published by Sony Interactive Entertainment Europe Limited. Developed by Saber Interactive.
